# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
 My first thought process to this problem was try to find the maximum sub array - in case if the total sum is greater then zero and the given k = 1 then in that situation the answer will be the total sum. 
and if k is greater than 1 then I will multiply the total sum with k and that will be my answer.
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1)Try to find the maximum sum of sub-array.
2)if (k == 1) return the maximum sum sub-array.
3)if k >= 2 in that case we have to find the maximum-suffix-sum and maximum prefix-sum and total-sum.
4)if total-sum >= 0 then in that case I will return maximum of 
max_prefix_sum+max_suffix_sum+total_sum*(k-2)[we are multiplying by k-2 because the first and last array is used for calculating the maximum prefix sum and maximum suffix sum respectively.] and kadaneSum,the maximum will be our answer.
5)if total_sum < 0 int that case we have to find maximum of max_prefix_sum+max_suffix_sum and kadanesum because if we take total-sum*(k-1) in this case the answer we will get is negative so there is no need to consider that part.
6)Finally we will return the ans .

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
 Time complexity = O(n)

- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
 Space complexity = O(1)
# Code
```
const int M = 1000000007;
#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
typedef long long ll;
class Solution {
public:
    int kadaneSum(vector<int>& arr)
    {
        ll mx = INT_MIN;
        ll sum = 0;
        for(int i = 0;i < arr.size();i++){
            sum = (sum + arr[i]) % M;
            if (sum < 0){
                sum = 0;
            }
            if (sum >= mx){
                mx = sum;
            }
        }
        return mx;
    }
    int kConcatenationMaxSum(vector<int>& arr, int k) {
        if (k == 1){
            return kadaneSum(arr);
        }
        ll prefix_sum = 0,suffix_sum = 0;
        ll max_prefix_sum = INT_MIN, max_suffix_sum = INT_MIN,total_sum=0;
          ll ans = kadaneSum(arr);
        if (k >= 2){
            for(int i = 0;i < arr.size();i++){
                prefix_sum += arr[i];
                if (prefix_sum > max_prefix_sum){
                    max_prefix_sum = prefix_sum;
                }
            }
              total_sum = prefix_sum%M;
             for(int i = arr.size()-1;i >= 0;i--){
                suffix_sum += arr[i];
                if (suffix_sum > max_suffix_sum){
                    max_suffix_sum = suffix_sum;
                }
            }

            if (total_sum >= 0){
                ans = max(ans,(max_prefix_sum+max_suffix_sum+total_sum*(k-2)));         
            }
            else{
                ans = max(ans,(max_prefix_sum+max_suffix_sum));    
            }


        }
     return ans%M;
    }


};
```

