Pick up the balls from block (Between level n and level n-1), it will have same cost. We will just need to multiply number of colors with number of balls to get our profit.

Keep slicing the bars on levels until our orders get fulfilled. 

Special case will be when the block size (which we will be slicing) is exceeding the number of orders, in this case we will only take the balls as per our requirement and won't slice the entire block.

