Breakdown the problem in sub problem and it will decode itself .Find a val which can get you atleast orders ball and try to find the sum of balls having weight greater than it + fulfill remaing balls equal to the least value.
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Sum(for a range m,m+1,m+2....m+n-1) is calclated using the formula (no of element)*(lower+upper)/2
Min weight needed is what we can get from binary search we will take all the balls above this values and fulfill remaining orderds from the balls with val we got from binary search
